	   <tr><td colspan=1 id=headerrow>Posted @ Thu, Aug 23rd 12:59 AM 2001</td>
	   <td id=headerrow align=right><span id=notbold>Score</span>: Default<span id=notbold>[2.00]</span></td></tr>
	   <tr><td colspan=2>Earth = Solo<br>Sta = Highest<br>Dex = Lowest<br>Agi = Lowest<br>Str = Highest<br>Class 51+ = Warrior<br>Spell = Root - Does damage 51+<br><br>Water = Solo/Group<br>Sta = High<br>Dex = High<br>Agi = High<br>Str = High<br>Class 51+ = Rogue - Ability Backstab<br>Spell = DD/Ice<br><br>Air = Duels/Group<br>Sta = Medium<br>Dex = Highest<br>Agi = Highest<br>STR = Medium<br>Class 51 = Monk<br>Spell = Stun - Does damage 51+<br><br>Fire = Sometimes Solo/Group<br>Sta = Lowest<br>Dex = High<br>Agi = Medium<br>Str = Low/Medium<br>Class 51+ = Wizard<br>Spells = DS - Strongest DD/Fire<br><br><br>--------------------------------------------------<br>Earth should only be used while soloing<br>--------------------------------------------------<br>1. Your root will stop enemys from runing causing it to hurt the group more then it should<br><br>2. It does not have any other ability to inflict damage like the other 3 do<br>--------------------------------------------------<br>Water good for Solo/Group<br>--------------------------------------------------<br>Solo<br>--------------------------------------------------<br>1. It have the ability to stay up longer then the other pets in most cases untill you gain your earths focus item<br><br>2. It has the ability to do more damage then your Earth pet untill 51+ <br>--------------------------------------------------<br>Group<br>--------------------------------------------------<br>1. Ability to give a group an extra tank<br><br>2. Does more Damage then any other pet 51+<br>--------------------------------------------------<br>Air Group<br>--------------------------------------------------<br>1. Ability to give the group an extra tank<br><br>2. Stuns enemys for awile (Casters)<br>--------------------------------------------------<br>Why it should not be used for soloing<br>--------------------------------------------------<br>1. the cast time for its stun is 12 seconds i would rather have a earth pets 6 second root hit then waiting an extra 6 seconds for the pet to save my ass on a bad nuke/pull or a heavy nuke from a fire pet<br>--------------------------------------------------<br>Fire Solo/Group<br>--------------------------------------------------<br>Solo<br>--------------------------------------------------<br>1. Its heavy DS(Taunt)Nuke Can make swift work of most enemys<br>--------------------------------------------------<br>Group<br>--------------------------------------------------<br>1. its DD can do some nice damage and its DS can hurt alot if its geting hit by something it can take on pretty well<br>--------------------------------------------------<br>WANRING: The fire pet cannot provide the group with an extra tank<br>--------------------------------------------------<br>Always keep your DS and BO spells on pet at all time 20+<br>--------------------------------------------------<br>Also make sure your earth pets root sticks a few times if it barly does use or not at all use your water pet<br>--------------------------------------------------<br>--------------------------------------------------<br><br><br>&nbsp;<br> </td></tr>
