	   <tr><td colspan=2>Personally, I would go bsck to our homeland of steamfont and solo the kobolds for a few levels, but if you don't want to ride the boat again (I wouldn't in your position) I would probably go to misty thicket. The experiance is great, the loot isn't bad, and the only real problems are the guards huge aggro radius that makes them ks mobs halfway across the zone. Or if you are brave you could go to the skellie camp in nektulos with a group. The inn in EC may be safe, but the XP is *very* slow killing level 1-2 mobs at level 4. I checked, you get about 1/16 of a blue (decent XP for my level 24 character) per kill on those mobs.<br><br>Kranken the crazy gnome of Xev<br>&nbsp;<br>Balidin Evilbasher<br>60 Paladin<br>Xev</td></tr>
