	   <tr><td colspan=2>ALL casters get the ability to cst bind affinity and gate. Bind affinity makes it so that when you die, you start up at the spot where you were binded. Gate lets you teleport to the spot where you are binded. <br><br>Wizards and Druids get teleportation spells that let them so other places besides where they are bound.<br><br>So yes, all casters get teleportation spells becuase of gate, but wizards and druids get the true teleportation spells.<br><br>Former EQ Addict.<br>&nbsp;<br></td></tr>
